@startuml
title Plane State Diagram

[*] --> Order

state "Order" as Order
state "Arrival" as Arrival
state "Preparation" as Preparation
state "Operations" as Operations
state "Maintenance" as Maintenance
state "Out of Service" as OutOfService
state "Withdrawn" as Withdrawn

Order --> Arrival : Plane delivered

Arrival --> Preparation : Plane arrived

Preparation --> Operations : Condition good and scheduled flights
Preparation --> Maintenance : Condition poor or no more scheduled flights

Operations --> Maintenance : Maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : Ready for operations

OutOfService --> [*] : Plane out of service
Withdrawn --> [*] : Plane withdrawn

@enduml
